{"tid":791879,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"[坐地起價正垃圾]勸大家咪撚幫襯PCCW","createTime":"2018-08-24T06:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T18:14:56.000Z","uid":9175,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7b64a0fd5675465a44218362fbc939ffd3e379e6","tid":791879,"uid":9175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T06:57:30.000Z","msg":"沒有最無恥，只有更無恥！！以前舊登聽過最仆街都係cut 唔倒有線啫 <br />\n估唔倒PCCW仲仆街未簽約已經想掠水，各位真係小心啲呢啲仆街公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的，話說朋友一直住喺坪洲，咁近日要搬去另一個單位，需要將寬頻線轉去新單位。<br />\n<br />\n前排朋友打電話上去網上行銷售部，同佢地傾有關事宜。當時員工稱由於朋友係舊客戶，應承可免搬遷費及月費$200，條件係簽2年約。<br />\n<br />\n但安裝前一日，相關員工再致電俾朋友，改稱要收取搬遷費($980)及月費改為$358，簽4年約。話說朋友喺坪洲居住了超過30年，一向都知道坪洲只有PCCW一間電訊公司可安裝寬頻，但PCCW員工就喺前一日玩野，明知情況喺咁咁突然坐地起價，實在可恥！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c43bf882135e774ed9723ca1ac46f9a9094f264","tid":791879,"uid":9175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:01:43.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 一定要推倒多啲人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3703d80ca192b3279a24d254b235943a09ac3dcf","tid":791879,"uid":9175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T07:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2615aa64394d92a8d023ef248860a4c629bd6514","tid":791879,"uid":9175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:38:31.000Z","msg":"點先可以多啲人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6cce674fae73debd1a3bb11cc2f27ccec4b242","tid":791879,"uid":72477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"無人想理<im